The paper deals with natural language processing tasks and deep learning techniques for answering multi-step reasoning questions on semi-structured tables. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Computer Science dealing with these topics, such as cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
